It could fall on a rocky path.

25:21.136 --> 25:26.203
It could fall on a thorny path or thorny soil or it could fall on good soil.

25:26.804 --> 25:32.973
It could fall on, sorry, hard path, a rocky soil, thorny soil, a good soil.

25:33.994 --> 25:42.706
And it says that basically the hard path is like when people just don't understand the scriptures and understand the word of God and the enemy will kind of come and snatch that up.

25:43.842 --> 25:50.430
The rocky path is that somebody might understand it and get really excited, but there's nothing deep root to kind of hold on to this.

25:50.450 --> 25:59.421
And so what ends up happening is when trouble times come, then the seeds of the kingdom of God don't first.

26:01.003 --> 26:10.754
Then there's a thorny path where if you like hear the word of God, but it's so preoccupied with the hustle of life and the deceitfulness of wealth, that the word of God gets choked out.

26:12.617 --> 26:13.778
And then the time with

26:14.050 --> 26:16.553
I know this is my biggest battle, right?

26:17.034 --> 26:18.115
It's that thorny path.

26:19.237 --> 26:36.400
But those that engage in cultivating the soil of their hearts with the word of God, the kingdom of God takes root and it takes its flourishes in their lives, in their heart and in their life.

26:38.743 --> 26:40.946
So what's the good news for the

26:41.122 --> 26:59.384
Those who might be deconstructing, it's good news to know that Jesus tells us in the parable of the weeds and the weeds, is that it's hard to determine who was going to hell and who was going to heaven.

27:01.847 --> 27:08.455
And that it's going to look very, sometimes it could look very similar and it's hard to know where's that happening.

27:08.475 --> 27:11.058
And so as humans, we aren't good judges on these things.

27:12.866 --> 27:34.734
But the thing that we can do is we can be gardeners in our own heart, that we can get away from the crowd, go to a place of intimacy, and ask Jesus questions that helps us to understand what is the kingdom of God, how to sow the words of the kingdom of God in our life and in our hearts.

27:36.316 --> 27:41.202
And then God can bring fruit 30, 60, and 100 fold.

27:42.530 --> 28:01.919
And that is what I want to pray for you all, that you all will be people that will seek to understand the Word of God, cultivate deep roots, and real allow God to be, to make you an agent of bringing heaven on earth.

28:02.900 --> 28:03.421
Let us pray.

28:08.909 --> 28:12.434
Well, I just thank you so much that

28:13.954 --> 28:15.676
there is a revealing that is happening.

28:17.138 --> 28:37.462
It feels like some level of a harvest where we're seeing that there are some saints and there are some aunts and that we need to stop judging one another, but to see, Lord, what is it that's going on in my own heart?

28:39.004 --> 28:40.626
