28:41.410 --> 28:43.893
How am I not applying your word in my life?

28:46.096 --> 28:52.905
I can't control my brother and my sister or the person on the internet, but what I can do is say, where's hypocrisy going on in my life?

28:54.788 --> 29:11.250
But I do pray for my brothers and sisters here at Bend, Oregon, here at Antioch that you would help those that might get a sense of feeling strong and if they've now to continue to cultivate in those that might feel weak to know this is part of the journey,

29:11.842 --> 29:23.463
And that you're inviting them to get away from the crowd, to find a place of intimacy, and to ask you questions because you love questions.

29:24.665 --> 29:26.308
